                    AI readiness audit and transformation roadmap development
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div
                  class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0"
                >
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">2</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                    Rapid Prototyping
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">
                    Proof-of-concept delivery in 4-6 weeks with measurable KPIs
                  </p>
